jain.protocol.ip.sip.header
Interface EndPointHeader

All Superinterfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, Header, NameAddressHeader, Parameters, ParametersHeader, java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
FromHeader, ToHeader
All Known Implementing Classes:
FromHeaderImpl, ToHeaderImpl
public interface EndPointHeader
extends NameAddressHeader

This interface represents any header that indicates an endpoint of a Message's path. It extends NameAddressHeader and is the super-interface of FromHeader and ToHeader.

See Also:
NameAddressHeader, FromHeader, ToHeader
